This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with the task of argument mining, which is a subfield of natural language processing. The paper also mentions the use of sentence-level queries and an iterative annotation scheme, which are common techniques used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.AI, cs.LG) respectively. Additionally, the paper deals with a large corpus of newspaper articles, which could fall under the sub-category of cs.CY (Computers and Society).
